<h1>Join</h1>
<p>Yearly membership (May through April) to the De Pere Sportsmen's Club is $80 and includes membership for a spouse and children under 18 years of age. The membership fee is no longer prorated, and all memberships renew in May, so be sure to join early in the year to get the most BANG! for the buck.</p>
<p>In order to join the De Pere Sportsmen's Club it is required that you watch a mandatory safety video at the time you submit your membership information and pay your dues. Effective May 2012, the Rifle Range guest fee is now $10 per day, per person. All guests must be accompanied by a paid member.</p>
<p>You may come down to the club to join on the 2nd Tuesday of every month at 6:00 pm. Please email your name, telephone number, and which 2nd Tuesday of the month you will be able to make it to <a href ="mailto:join@deperesportsmensclub.com">join@deperesportsmensclub.com</a>.  If we receive no emails prior to the 2nd Tuesday of the month, we will not hold the new membership sign up.</p>
